WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.315
Myocarditis — inflammation of the myocardium —

00:00:03.315 --> 00:00:06.629
presents a spectrum from subclinical disease to

00:00:06.629 --> 00:00:08.050
fulminant hemodynamic collapse.

00:00:08.050 --> 00:00:11.365
This clinical review focuses on adverse effects,

00:00:11.365 --> 00:00:14.679
prognostic risk factors, and evidence-based management for

00:00:14.679 --> 00:00:16.100
the practicing physician.
